data.description: This charming 4 bedroom, 2 full bath, brick home offers tons of space, an updated kitchen, updated bathroom fixtures, a new hot water heater, insulated walls and ceiling fans. Having lots of light and an open concept, it also features a mother-in-law suite which can be entered into from the screened in back porch as well as having its own entrance from back yard.  Located close to downtown which makes everything including shopping and dining easy to get to. Ready to make it your own? Gas stove stays as well as refrigerator and washer/dryer.
